mysql-router: MySQL Router (a lightweight middleware for routing MySQL traffic)
mysql-router:
mysql-router: MySQL Router is lightweight middleware that provides transparent
mysql-router: routing between your application and any backend MySQL Servers.
mysql-router: It can be used for a wide variety of use cases, such as providing
mysql-router: high availability and scalability by effectively routing database
mysql-router: traffic to appropriate backend MySQL Servers.
